                        "requirement": "A grabbed, paralyzed, restrained, unconscious, or willing creature is within reach of the asanbosam\u2019s jaws.",
                        "effect": "The asanbosam sinks its teeth into the creature to drink its blood. If the victim is grabbed, this is automatic; otherwise, the asanbosam must succeed at an Athletics check against the victim\u2019s Fortitude DC. The victim becomes drained 1 and the asanbosam regains 10 HP, gaining any excess HP as temporary Hit Points. Drinking Blood from a creature that\u2019s already drained increases the victim\u2019s drained value by 1, but doesn\u2019t restore any HP to the asanbosam.<br/> A victim\u2019s drained condition decreases by 1 each week. A blood transfusion, which requires a successful DC 20 Medicine check and a blood donor or sufficient blood, reduces the drained value by 1 after 10 minutes."
